ItemBGDesc: The Light Cone gifted by the Garden of Recollection to March 7th. The memory sealed within is none other than her "origin." "An eagle borne on mighty wings will never miss the cliffs it once fell from, and a full-mast ship will never miss the beach where she once ran aground. And you, my child, know that the past is as intangible as a hazy mirage. But everything you are experiencing right now will surely be etched in stone by those who come after."
